{"id":256261,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/奇闻录-光标戴绿帽作法送车/","date":"2012-10-11T02:46:14Z","modified":"2012-10-11T02:50:40Z","title":"奇闻录 | 光标戴绿帽作法送车","content":"<p>10月10日，陈光标为43个在抗日保钓事件中被砸的日系车主换车，每人赠送一辆价值12.8万的国产汽车。陈光标呼吁在场的受助者和员工要理性爱国，保护环境。陈光标让美女给他戴上绿帽子，然后又站在车顶又唱又跳并摆出各种造型，并引领全场人士高唱“我爱你中国”，最后还摆出一张将他形象PS在钓鱼岛上的巨幅画像。</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"陈光标出资500万给被砸车车主换国产新车\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201094_280590.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img title=\"陈光标赠车1\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/thumbs/thumbs_2841_201094_280590.jpg\" alt=\"陈光标赠车1\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /> </a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"陈光标在南京举行以旧车换新车活\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201095_192591.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img title=\"陈光标赠车2\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/thumbs/thumbs_2841_201095_192591.jpg\" alt=\"陈光标赠车2\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /> </a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"陈光标要求受助者要用拿枪的姿势领取车钥匙模型\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201096_893698.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img title=\"陈光标赠车3\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/thumbs/thumbs_2841_201096_893698.jpg\" alt=\"陈光标赠车3\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /> </a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"换车活动现场\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201097_641662.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img title=\"陈光标赠车4\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/thumbs/thumbs_2841_201097_641662.jpg\" alt=\"陈光标赠车4\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /> </a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"美女给陈光标戴绿帽\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201098_491406.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img title=\"陈光标赠车5\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/thumbs/thumbs_2841_201098_491406.jpg\" alt=\"陈光标赠车5\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" /> </a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a title=\"陈光标站在车顶又唱又跳并摆出各种造型\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/cgbsc/2841_201099_500039